A Debian package can be generated from this directory tree with the commands:

  mkdir -p ~/packaging/python-cdx && \
  cp -r ~/workspace/snacs/cdx_format/python ~/packaging/python-cdx/python-cdx_1.0 && \
  cd ~/packaging/python-cdx && \
  tar czf python-cdx_1.0.orig.tar.gz python-cdx_1.0 && \
  cd python-cdx_1.0 && \
  debuild -us -uc

Installation on Mac OS X
========================

In snacs/cdx_format/python run
  sudo /opt/local/bin/python2 setup.py install
